OL,3,C'It ruins you': the impact of being
OL,4,Cindefinitely imprisoned
OL,6,FA former prisoner says his experience
OL,7,Fof serving an open-ended, indefinite
OL,8,Fsentence "ruined" him and he is still
OL,9,Ftaking medication to deal with the
OL,10,Fimpact years after his release.
OL,12,FFormer inmate Ben was told he would
OL,13,Fserve a minimum of 2 years but ended
OL,14,Fup in prison for 14 years. It is an
OL,15,Fexperience he says has left him with
OL,16,Flife-long mental scars.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
