OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776280294
OL,3,C'It ruins you': the impact of being
OL,4,Cindefinitely imprisoned
OL,6,FIn 2022, after a three-year-long
OL,7,Finquiry, the Justice Select Committee
OL,8,Fcalled on the government to resentence
OL,9,Fall IPPs still in prison. The system
OL,10,Fwas described as "irredeemably flawed"
OL,11,Fand causing inmates to self-harm.
OL,13,FIn response, the then Conservative
OL,14,Fgovernment said it wasn't going to
OL,15,Fresentence IPPs, but would review the
OL,16,Flicensing conditions for those who are
OL,17,Freleased.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776280294
OL,3,C'It ruins you': the impact of being
OL,4,Cindefinitely imprisoned
OL,6,FIn 2024, reforms allowed IPP offenders
OL,7,Fwho were released from custody at
OL,8,Fleast 5 years ago but not sent back to
OL,9,Fprison in the last 2 years to have
OL,10,Ftheir licences automatically
OL,11,Fterminated. According to the Ministry
OL,12,Fof Justice, this affected 1,800
OL,13,Frehabilitated offenders.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776280294
OL,3,C'It ruins you': the impact of being
OL,4,Cindefinitely imprisoned
OL,6,FFurther changes, which were effective
OL,7,Ffrom 1 February 2025, cut the
OL,8,Feligibility period for the Parole
OL,9,FBoard to consider ending licences from
OL,10,F10 years after first release to 3,
OL,11,Fwhich made an additional 600 former
OL,12,Foffenders eligible to have their
OL,13,Flicenses ended.
OL,15,FChanges are due to come into force in
OL,16,FJune this year which will mean that
OL,17,Fthose serving an IPP sentence will be
OL,18,Fconsidered for licence termination two
OL,19,Fyears after release ` rather than the
OL,20,Fcurrent three years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776280294
OL,3,C'It ruins you': the impact of being
OL,4,Cindefinitely imprisoned
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Justice has said it is
OL,7,Fbalancing important public protections
OL,8,Fwith the need to move offenders who
OL,9,Fhave turned their lives around out of
OL,10,Fprison and off licence.
OL,12,FWhen addressing families' concerns
OL,13,Fahead of Wednesday's protest, it said:
OL,14,F"It is right that IPP sentences were
OL,15,Fabolished, and we have already taken
OL,16,Faction to support these offenders to
OL,17,Fmove on with their lives.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776280294
OL,3,C'It ruins you': the impact of being
OL,4,Cindefinitely imprisoned
OL,6,F"We are changing the law to ensure
OL,7,Fthose serving these sentences in the
OL,8,Fcommunity can be more swiftly
OL,9,Fconsidered for licence termination."
OL,26,@qD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
